Uses of Class
team11.core.other.Shot

  • Packages that use Shot 
    Package Description
    team11.core.agent
    This package provides the abstract Angry Birds AI agent, Team11Agent, which an implementation of this jar file agent must extends.
    team11.core.other
    This package provides a few other structures including; an environment access file, and the Shot object used when shooting birds from the sling-shot.
    team11.core.schema
    This package provides the set of schemas used when interfacing with the game itself.
    team11.core.utils
    This package provides the utilities for connections, actions, and processing an implementation may require.
